Class HospitalStaff

java.lang.Object
entity.EntityObject
entity.user.User
entity.user.HospitalStaff
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Doctor, Pharmacist
public class HospitalStaff extends User
The HospitalStaff class represents a staff member of the hospital, who is a user of the system with a specific role (e.g., Doctor, Pharmacist, Administrator). This class extends the User class and adds additional properties like role and age.
